system.description:
These submachine guns were an old design, even before the War, and while they’re hideously inaccurate, their rate-of-fire means you don’t need to be accurate.

A Submachine Gun can accept one each of the following mods:

  • Receiver: Hardened, Hair Trigger, Powerful
  • Stock: Full Stock, Recoil-Compensating Stock
  • Magazine: Large Magazine, Quick-Eject Magazine, Large Quick-Eject Magazine
  • Sights: Reflex Sight
  • Muzzle: Compensator, Muzzle Brake, Suppressor
